{"tid":1818802,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"有手足因拒絕篤灰被施以酷刑後遭槍殺","createTime":"2020-01-10T08:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T14:12:56.000Z","uid":82235,"like":835,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"9669c75c80e13a082df3c1c78af714a5da979b1b","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:19:02.000Z","msg":"佢叫湯德章，臺南人，係人權義務律師<br />\n1947年、於二二八事件中<br />\n因拒絕交出「暴徒名單」，<br />\n最終被國民黨軍隊公開槍決<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5sLiuwxlfTE&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5sLiuwxlfTE%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=a9a10421\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5sLiuwxlfTE&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n因為湯德章以血肉為盾<br />\n隻身擋下數以千計手足被清算屠殺嘅命運<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歷史總是驚人地相似<br />\n係228鎮壓事件有一幕：<br />\n國民黨軍隊於八堵火車站<br />\n無差別槍殺平民<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pU5QJV_SRj8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpU5QJV_SRj8&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=53870aea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pU5QJV_SRj8</a><br />\n<br />\n時空交錯73年，香港太子831<br />\n黑警恐襲、殺人封站、再濫捕悼念者<br />\n<br />\n今日國國難忠醫廣州被捕<br />\n會唔會係因為要佢交出「暴徒名單」？<br />\n<br />\n臺灣由228大屠殺起、進入白色恐怖戒嚴時期，<br />\n歷時38年，平民上街、然後，就沒然後<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道台灣年輕一代有幾多人切切實實感受到<br />\n自己手上果一票所包含嘅血汗、性命同重量<br />\n我只係自私地希望佢哋可以幫手守住我地僅餘嘅小小希望<br />\n<br />\n但係我知道今日好多香港人<br />\n都仲未了解到我地已經身陷戒嚴時代<br />\n好多手足已經付出左佢哋嘅前途、血肉、生命<br />\n好似煙花咁照亮平常人嘅歌舞昇平生活如常<br />\n但係煙花轉眼燒盡嘅時候、剩低嘅就只有無盡夜晚嘅黑暗<br />\n<br />\n香港係呢半年，有幾多千人被自殺、被消失、被捕、被虐<br />\n我地又經唔經得起咁樣嘅日子過38年？<br />\n而呢樣係唔係大家成日講嘅長期戰？留力？聽日見？<br />\n係唔係大家因為唔忍心而講嘅唔值得？不受傷？不被捕？<br />\n<br />\n有啲嘢、依家唔做，以後就冇機會再做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人，反抗。<br />\n<br />\n你做盡未？"},{"pid":"696fcfb3283fe5a545e612b03d1068bbdce1f227","tid":1818802,"uid":76314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2bf042a61ee28274c53a6fff8eacb081b702cd1","tid":1818802,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:25:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36bea69c8f6c48327305ef7795a75d75d7a5c3b5","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:26:53.000Z","msg":"在黑警被法律制裁之前<br />\n所謂法律皆為不法之法<br />\n<br />\n不公不義之極權暴政<br />\n冇資格判決手足有罪無罪"},{"pid":"d5c5b945c05801324ece8dc2130989eedf1cafad","tid":1818802,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab27cfdaf1e9898719e6939efdf184d1f423ad3","tid":1818802,"uid":64073,"like":37,"dislike":27,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:29:04.000Z","msg":"標題黨"},{"pid":"e568e7c2acb9fa6cb9d7931202fcc94aba0629b1","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:29:29.000Z","msg":"法治係要經人民授權、<br />\n以法律管束公權力<br />\n<br />\n極權獨裁之法<br />\n等同家法，係逼害公民嘅工具"},{"pid":"dd7724d8a2c376eb7c6cdd3a3ea870b0e2d3b22a","tid":1818802,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:29:31.000Z","msg":"仲返大陸做乜?"},{"pid":"087b4b1cbb682698c2b05f9b6487138c723dfd07","tid":1818802,"uid":192824,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:31:23.000Z","msg":"個律師好偉大，"},{"pid":"3c62a6ccb3868d6ae64b73be3a02e1fd1f7a315d","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:31:43.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，係法治基礎<br />\n唔可能由獨裁體制內改革施捨"},{"pid":"b55c6c6c837cbff4a8d085801f3f057be30d05b2","tid":1818802,"uid":186020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:32:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f09fcd2eca1cb2819f2824a548d68ffc17d131f8","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:33:32.000Z","msg":"重複訴求，和平上街，然後重返秩序<br />\n只會係永劫輪迴"},{"pid":"44b3b3fcab05d89acaa73b893573f358ed6a4c15","tid":1818802,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f5afdc4f2122031b5f79dd3ca5cb1758892acd8b","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:36:41.000Z","msg":"我哋要擴闊對勇武嘅想像<br />\n係每個崗位上全力反抗<br />\n以推翻政權為目標<br />\n<br />\n守法者口中講嘅偽法治<br />\n係我地最需要提防嘅遮醜布<br />\n<br />\n獨裁之法非法治<br />\n唔可以比司法轉移焦點"},{"pid":"acf1b529f85d25d04c8b01f64b6248c430309756","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"963ced8518fe5a4efb3db95cf67400d389774742","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:40:45.000Z","msg":"昨日臺灣<br />\n今日香港"},{"pid":"ade1fae6fb3a787a8591621177d04131596b9a74","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:42:34.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門"},{"pid":"dbadfefac3b6bc5aa4e2907c0a16c53f19d2a709","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:42:48.000Z","msg":"不能只有我看到"},{"pid":"ad52b7cff98dc04bf74c62aaafcbaeb541744e00","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:44:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6755a23add938120c24bff568e084af3bec5b09","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:48:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5234272189250d122720cd654d8ae4ab1f3995a","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:50:00.000Z","msg":"係呢半年入面被消失嘅手足<br />\n處境又有何不同？"},{"pid":"051a839f7dcf1da2caf81cc62133b1e7b3d30bce","tid":1818802,"uid":321674,"like":0,"disl