,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ef807e54aa229861c914b0e9f60c07a78eade0","tid":1818802,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跨時空手足"},{"pid":"d762053a138ae1bbfd6ac846aebd7a8013393fb4","tid":1818802,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:41:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcfef693d39bf755c959c6e649a46b6e63aab928","tid":1818802,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:41:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1963813d0a6c0066f4225c57ee7f5724c2bce7e","tid":1818802,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好人一生平安"},{"pid":"d4e826391268985ee178bd3eed026143817465a5","tid":1818802,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:41:50.000Z","msg":"Must Push"},{"pid":"8e48a9b009b9c5e43657425905dd7e7e6cece8aa","tid":1818802,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:42:06.000Z","msg":"Always stand with Doctor"},{"pid":"f35454ea8972a22927e14d5cb6a601cfd0197408","tid":1818802,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:42:16.000Z","msg":"借個位宣傳吸引火力黎推post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nfor 想健康升級/心態體力提升手足參考<br />\n<br />\n入黎補補正能量調整心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人夠正能量先頂到落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自衞隊身體質素＆勇氣全世界都大有必要<br />\n香港人 only you can change yourself<br />\n未來嘅希望由我地做起<br />\n<br />\nStep 10.心存希望 管理情緒<br />\nHeal yourself🌱<br />\nFree yourself 🈵<br />\nFree the emotion🎉<br />\n無論咩時間 心存希望<br />\n我的使命係帶希望比大家<br />\n我地一齊行落去 <br />\n沒有處理不到的事<br />\n只有處理不到的心情<br />\n管理好情緒 有助我地做得更好<br />\n⚡️減少重複接觸影響自己的負面人事<br />\n🍎每日練習 突破舒適圈 比自己進步一下<br />\n🔥要增肌/提神/搵工/調理身體想心情更好歡迎黎搵我運動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：健康教練<br />\n啱嘅就聽下幫自己再幫人<br />\n 唔啱聽我都唔會覆你 <br />\n重點係大家Build up自信＋能耐做更強嘅自己 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">We can do it</span></span> <br />\n香港人團結 正能量<br />\n呢個世界唔係我地影響人<br />\n就係人地影響緊我地<br />\n我地要內在夠強 大返佢地<br />\n<br />\n永續健康身心 成功致勝<br />\n營養/心態歡迎搵我幫手<br />\n教完大家要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港需要大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTG ME幫你Case Study <br />\n教你點飲食點運動打仗飲食法<br />\n20％運動 80％營養<br />\n學完再善用Budget 搞好自己體能<br />\n支持升級黃圈 培訓人才人人出資資助小朋友就業<br />\n免費簡單健康分析<br />\n收費嘅跟進我都做 <br />\n支持黃圈返正價出錢幫人<br />\nNothing is free for granted <br />\nIf you Learn, do help more ppl<br />\n得閒係屋企/搵我做下運動放鬆<br />\nBuild up 自己自信 無狗敢搞你<br />\n如果你期望唔出付就會有結果<br />\n請你離開<br />\n<br />\nMy TG<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTreeHoIsGood&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=a9c91a86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TreeHoIsGood</a><br />\nChannel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FtreehoHealthAdvice&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=7f7c688e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/treehoHealthAdvice</a><br />\n討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/THHATalk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTHHATalk&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=68fec1f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/THHATalk</a><br />\n長期戰爭 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對抗白色恐怖 <br />\n反共抗中 我地勢不兩立<br />\nWe Shall Never Surrender<br />\n<br />\nUnited, We can win the fight"},{"pid":"882761ce801f75ebe2af4365975c161cf60d8a06","tid":1818802,"uid":224829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:42:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53213a43afd186d87cb6d12b2b7d51796c1191ba","tid":1818802,"uid":8091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:42:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d414448cfd984ac651951915874342bd0d77214","tid":1818802,"uid":165871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"987e60e4d1a494046d7371ae92121c0d27f887a8","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b6b2515d68e31c3a3e331d1f4237215d38108075","tid":1818802,"uid":165871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6834d4c46f21591968add3e8b243a2b16f0a628","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8456a81060b1b3de8bb78f56e16eca5c505836e6","tid":1818802,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"歷史會不斷重複<br />\n<br />\n香港人準備好未？<br />\n<br />\n台灣的朋友如果在看這個Post ，請你們不要讓自己再回到戒嚴的時代"},{"pid":"8d4c4f87993adfce30a3a26c445c781e45f5553f","tid":1818802,"uid":29643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"推動"},{"pid":"c8cc2fa1812f31559ed8bd5ef25a78278762ac2a","tid":1818802,"uid":293896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20