{SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YE6xnMC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYE6xnMC.jpg&h=84559772&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gkLqHMD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgkLqHMD.jpg&h=5036ec9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃店賀年食品</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rY7TRFB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrY7TRFB.png&h=7e3a6ef2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0808141f30454f7c81e62c7c1b42c0301d670335","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:42:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f7a2d2244a868ea069d9c0bff586f462197e52e","tid":1818802,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9669c75c80e13a082df3c1c78af714a5da979b1b","tid":1818802,"uid":82235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:19:02.000Z","msg":"佢叫湯德章，臺南人，係人權義務律師<br />\n1947年、於二二八事件中<br />\n因拒絕交出「暴徒名單」，<br />\n最終被國民黨軍隊公開槍決<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5sLiuwxlfTE&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5sLiuwxlfTE%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=a9a10421\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5sLiuwxlfTE&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n因為湯德章以血肉為盾<br />\n隻身擋下數以千計手足被清算屠殺嘅命運<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歷史總是驚人地相似<br />\n係228鎮壓事件有一幕：<br />\n國民黨軍隊於八堵火車站<br />\n無差別槍殺平民<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pU5QJV_SRj8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpU5QJV_SRj8&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=53870aea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pU5QJV_SRj8</a><br />\n<br />\n時空交錯73年，香港太子831<br />\n黑警恐襲、殺人封站、再濫捕悼念者<br />\n<br />\n今日國國難忠醫廣州被捕<br />\n會唔會係因為要佢交出「暴徒名單」？<br />\n<br />\n臺灣由228大屠殺起、進入白色恐怖戒嚴時期，<br />\n歷時38年，平民上街、然後，就沒然後<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道台灣年輕一代有幾多人切切實實感受到<br />\n自己手上果一票所包含嘅血汗、性命同重量<br />\n我只係自私地希望佢哋可以幫手守住我地僅餘嘅小小希望<br />\n<br />\n但係我知道今日好多香港人<br />\n都仲未了解到我地已經身陷戒嚴時代<br />\n好多手足已經付出左佢哋嘅前途、血肉、生命<br />\n好似煙花咁照亮平常人嘅歌舞昇平生活如常<br />\n但係煙花轉眼燒盡嘅時候、剩低嘅就只有無盡夜晚嘅黑暗<br />\n<br />\n香港係呢半年，有幾多千人被自殺、被消失、被捕、被虐<br />\n我地又經唔經得起咁樣嘅日子過38年？<br />\n而呢樣係唔係大家成日講嘅長期戰？留力？聽日見？<br />\n係唔係大家因為唔忍心而講嘅唔值得？不受傷？不被捕？<br />\n<br />\n有啲嘢、依家唔做，以後就冇機會再做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人，反抗。<br />\n<br />\n你做盡未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622a145992be4fb7f149f5a6f05f77ae5540fbf6","tid":1818802,"uid":145621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:57:14.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"92f3f4fc46b9e29271307aea5d15abcdaec56037","tid":1818802,"uid":159796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:58:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49dbd2b7549000c2d59e40135c377101f7ea5141","tid":1818802,"uid":171480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48262185dbcd2fd8aa12face6078f39f5f6cb08","tid":1818802,"uid":220985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41392c66fec5bff589f2d9a0297ce51a5cc3c44a","tid":1818802,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:14:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2eb0fb778e93625612a1776f86d8d8dc92a32067","tid":1818802,"uid":54220,